thread.title: Marc Whaley
thread.title_full: SecurCare Self Storage reviewed by Marc Whaley

author: Marc Whaley
title: Marc Whaley
text:
My experience with SecureCare was great, facility was clean and well maintained and the storage unit itself was in very good shape.
My only negative is that the keypad at the exit needs to be replaced, it is rubberized and you have to punch the numbers in extremely hard - it takes several tries to get it to work.
SecureCare
3218 S Garnett Road
Tulsa, OK 74146
